### List
GET http://localhost:3007/api/cart

### Add
POST http://localhost:3007/api/cart
Content-Type: application/json

{ "product_id": 1, "quantity": 2 }

### Clear
DELETE http://localhost:3007/api/cart

### Verb not in map → 405 with Allow header.
PUT http://localhost:3007/api/cart
Content-Type: application/json

{ "anything": true }
